{
  "stem": "1873.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 539.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the time did come that his wife and children were liquidated to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was still a German, so they didn't touch him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he was trying to go to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they arrested him in Stryj in the train, [INAUDIBLE] verify.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He told the story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The next day, I remember, we were in one room like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You could hear it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The lawyer told him, listen, Mr.-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Lippman, if I would be in your place, I wouldn't sit a minute in the jail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were-- they were asking the guard for the papers, for some paper and a pencil.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the way the lawyer dictate him, they wrote a letter to Governor Hanks-- Frank's office in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Probably, the letter didn't go to Krakow, to Frank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Probably, the gestapo in the jail did in-- get the letter, because it took two days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we heard some steps in the hallway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the steps stopped in front of our door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the door opened, and there were two SS officers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they look around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they say, Herr-- Herr Alvin Lippman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Herr, that sounded already optimistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because to a Jew, they never said that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Take your stuff and come with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he grabbed his stuff, and the SS are looking around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they asked the Kommandant-- the Kommandant-- the Kommandant for the jail was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His same was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And an hour later, the guards did come, took us-- took us down and took us to the next jail.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next jail, it wasn't a good place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Me and Wolf and the rest of the Jews in our group, were pushed in a big room, was a huge room, about a 100 people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
